mcqs.question:
What is the output of compiling this code?
class Test {
 final int x;
 Test() { x = 10; }
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 System.out.println(new Test().x);
 }
}

What is the output?
class Parent {
 final void show() { System.out.println("Parent"); }
}
class Child extends Parent {
 void show() { System.out.println("Child"); }
}
public class Main {
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 new Child().show();
 }
}

What is the output?
class Test {
 static final int x;
 static { x = 50; }
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 System.out.println(x);
 }
}
